Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.92,0:01:41.92,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}正体不明の引力が常識を無に帰す
