Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.76,0:01:48.76,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}冗談じゃねえよ Phantom's begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.97,0:01:50.97,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,500)\blur2\be1}嘘にまみれきって蜃気楼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.51,0:01:53.52,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}心まで霞んで蜃気楼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:56.69,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}善々悪々も審議不能になる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.94,0:02:00.94,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}全部嫌になった　それさえも幸せな結末だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.57,0:02:05.57,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}だめだ　そんな悲しいこと言うな　まだ世界は生きてる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.86,0:02:07.86,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}君が泣いてたって生きてる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.53,0:02:10.53,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}だからこの空の先を見たい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.50,0:02:15.50,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}邪魔すぎる運命のターゲット睨みながら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.71,0:02:19.71,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,800)\blur2\be1}言えそうで良かった「まだ愛していたい」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.85,0:01:11.85,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}為錯位的焦點所惑 四下尋找說辭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.31,0:01:14.31,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}看吧枯葉起舞 終會化為蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.73,0:01:15.73,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}然後調節到位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.31,0:01:17.31,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,0)\blur2\be1}然後是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.40,0:01:21.40,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}時過境遷太急 秒速開始不合理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.90,0:01:23.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}全因自己武斷的選擇開端
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.07,0:01:26.07,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}所以必須做出了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.82,0:01:29.83,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}無聊的理由 是停止思考的鐵證
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.12,0:01:33.12,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}無法守護應守護之物 那就不要亂出頭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.04,0:01:38.04,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}共鳴 榮光 稱讚 都不應奢求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.92,0:01:41.92,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}不明真相的引力 將常識歸於虛無
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.92,0:01:43.92,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}會扣下扳機
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.76,0:01:48.76,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}不是開玩笑的 幻覺已經開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.97,0:01:50.97,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,500)\blur2\be1}充滿謊言的海市蜃樓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.51,0:01:53.52,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}讓心都變得模糊的海市蜃樓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:56.69,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}善善惡惡都無法評議
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.94,0:02:00.94,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}全都變得討厭 連這都是幸福的結局
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.57,0:02:05.57,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}不行 不要說得如此悲涼 世界依然活著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.86,0:02:07.86,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}即使你會哭泣也還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.53,0:02:10.53,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}所以想看到這片天空的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.50,0:02:15.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}一邊瞪視過於礙眼的命運的目標
